items.title: Ex-Nigerian President Buhari to be buried at home
items.description: Muhammadu Buhari, who was both a military ruler and elected president, died in London on Sunday.

items.title: First Indian astronaut to visit ISS returns to Earth
items.description: The Axiom-4 (Ax-4) mission with Shubhanshu Shukla splashed down off the coast of California.

items.title: Aid workers 'executed' in Ethiopia's Tigray war, charity says
items.description: A Spaniard and two Ethiopians were shot dead during the conflict in northern Ethiopia, MSF says.

items.title: 'Not our war' - Trump's Nato weapons deal for Ukraine sparks MAGA anger
items.description: Marjorie Taylor Greene, a key Trump ally, and former Trump strategist Steve Bannon have criticised the move.

items.title: I'm 'disappointed but not done' with Putin, Trump tells BBC
items.description: Trump says he trusts "almost nobody" in exclusive interview discussing the war in Ukraine, Nato and the UK.
